{"tid":1051984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美中打貿易戰　賴正鎰：台灣重回四小龍之首好時機","createTime":"2019-03-08T04:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T04:12:55.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9d92f578e224238733f643a9023ab7422b8db461","tid":1051984,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7238/3658557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7238%2F3658557&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=0ded65bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7238/3658557</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/12/6/5913624.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F12%2F6%2F5913624.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=6e933d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商總理事長賴正鎰。 記者侯永全/攝影<br />\n<br />\n全國商總理事長賴正鎰今（22）日在媒體新春記者會上指出，肥咖條款加上美中貿易戰，促使海外游資與台商加速返台投資，台灣再度站上決勝浪尖，是重回亞洲四小龍之首的好時機，他已經感受到拚經濟的巨大能量，政府要有更宏觀的創新戰略與政策，吸引海內外企業加速投資台灣。"}]}